<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Reservation Confirmation</title>
</head>
<body>
<h1>Hello, {{ user }}!</h1>
<p>Thank you for reserving your seats at our cinema.</p>
<p>Film: <strong>{{ film }}</strong></p>
<p>Reserved Seats: <strong>{{ seats|join(', ') }}</strong></p>
<p>Total Price: <strong>${{ total_price }}</strong></p>
<p>We hope you enjoy the show!</p>
<p>Best regards,<br>The Cinema Team</p>
</body>
</html>